<lb n="0922a04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0922a05" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1406</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0922a06" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0922001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本</note>佛說辟除賊害&CB00057;經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0922a07" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0922a08" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0922a0801"><note n="0922002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">南無前行元本明本俱有舊失譯人名今附東晉錄</note>南無佛南無法南無比丘僧。南無過去七佛。
<lb n="0922a09" ed="T"/>南無諸佛南無諸佛弟子。南無諸師南無諸
<lb n="0922a10" ed="T"/>師弟子。南無默利薛利鬼神王。禮是已便說
<lb n="0922a11" ed="T"/>是&CB00057;。令我所&CB00057;皆從如願。</p>
<lb n="0922a12" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0922a1201">北方有山名<note n="0922003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">健＝犍【三】</note><note n="0922003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">健＝犍【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0922003"><lem wit="【大】">健</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">犍</rdg></app>陀摩訶<note n="0922004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">術＝衍【三】</note><note n="0922004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">術＝衍【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0922004"><lem wit="【大】">術</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">衍</rdg></app>。有鬼神王名默利
<lb n="0922a13" ed="T"/><note n="0922005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">陰＝薜【元】【明】</note><app n="0922005"><lem wit="【大】">陰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">薜</rdg></app>利居止彼。</p>
<lb n="0922a14" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0922a1401">有四姊弟。何等為四。</p>
<lb n="0922a15" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0922a1501" type="dharani">安檀尼　閻摩尼　<note n="0922006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB04369;＝&CB08057;【三】＊</note><note n="0922006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB04369;＝&CB08057;【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0922006"><lem wit="【大】">&CB04369;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&CB08057;</rdg></app>摩尼　無呵尼　安
<lb n="0922a16" ed="T"/>檀尼　令賊目盲　<note n="0922007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無訶＝閻摩【三】</note><note n="0922007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無訶＝閻摩【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0922007"><lem wit="【大】">無訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">閻摩</rdg></app>尼　令賊住　<app source="0922006" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB04369;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&CB08057;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0922a17" ed="T"/>摩尼　令賊坐　無呵尼　令賊愚癡　癡如
<lb n="0922a18" ed="T"/>是　漚羅利　無羅利　壇坻遮　波頭摩
<lb n="0922a19" ed="T"/>　遮迦利　當使賊　口齒噤　至解縷　乃得
<lb n="0922a20" ed="T"/>脫</p>
<lb n="0922a21" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0922a2101">說如是&CB00057;已。便言我為某甲若干人等。作擁
<lb n="0922a22" ed="T"/>護辟邪害皆令得安隱。</p>
<lb n="0922a23" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0922a2301">始諷誦是經時。當用月二十九日。於佛前然
<lb n="0922a24" ed="T"/>七燈燒。膠香散花說。是&CB00057;七<note n="0922008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">過＝遍【三】＊</note><note n="0922008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">過＝遍【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0922008"><lem wit="【大】">過</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">遍</rdg></app>并。&CB00057;願默
<lb n="0922a25" ed="T"/>利羅鬼神王使得福德亦。為然燈燒香<note n="0922009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔散〕－【宋】</note><app n="0922009"><lem wit="【大】">散</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">&lac;</rdg></app>花
<lb n="0922a26" ed="T"/>復為鬼子母然七燈燒香散花亦。當說是經
<lb n="0922a27" ed="T"/>七<app source="0922008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">過</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">遍</rdg></app>後。&CB00057;乃<note n="0922010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">告＝吉【三】</note><note n="0922010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">告＝吉【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0922010"><lem wit="【大】">告</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">吉</rdg></app>當如是語即。從如願。</p>
<lb n="0922a28" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><note n="0922011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">末題新加</note>佛說辟除賊害&CB00057;經</jhead></juan></div1>
